Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:33.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mình sẽ trả gấp hai mươi lần!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Không thể để đứa nào mó tay vào được!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mình sẽ bảo vệ quần chíp của Panty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:37.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:58.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}Heaven, please sing for me a song of life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:03.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}Heaven, take me into your skies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:07.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}There's no place here for me to hide my cries
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:11.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}Night and day, I'm missing you (ooh)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:15.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}You're so close, so close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:18.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}And it's you that I believe in, I believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:23.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}So close, but faraway, so far I can't touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}I'll hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:27.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}'Cuz it's you I love so dearly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:30.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}When the rain, the storm, and all is done
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\blur2\fad(100,200)}Caress me with your sweet lullaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:36.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:58.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thiên đường, xin hãy cất lên bài ca của cuộc sống
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:03.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thiên đường, hãy đưa tôi đến bầu trời xa xăm kia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:07.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nơi đây không có chỗ để giấu đi những giọt lệ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:11.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ngày lẫn đêm, tôi đều nhớ về người
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:15.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thật gần, sao thật gần
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:18.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Và người là điều tôi tin, tôi mãi tin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:23.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thật gần gũi, mà cũng thật xa xôi, ngoài tầm tay bé nhỏ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sẽ giữ chặt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:27.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vì người là tình yêu mãnh liệt của tôi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:30.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Khi cơn mưa, gió bão khẽ trôi qua
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hãy vuốt ve tôi bằng lời ru ngọt ngào ấy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
